headline.main: Trump, Offering No Evidence, Says Obama Tapped His Phones
headline.print_headline: With No Proof,Trump Claims Obama Tapped

lead_paragraph: Britain's foreign secretary will soon travel to Russia on a visit his office says will be consistent with the country's "engage but beware" policy toward Moscow.
